haiku:
Oh, Little Tokyo
Temples, sushi and the mall
Now with GA too!

A cool place I like
It's a good place to hangout.
Must try the mezcal

Bonaventure bar
Revolves around and around
Will it make me sick?

i like lots of cats,
they are small, cute, fun, and fast
and they like treats too.

All fans gather here
Dodgers, expensive hotdogs
And they lose again!

No one likes the valley,
Suburbs, traffic and the heat
Better have a pool!
Waiting for the first snowfall in Big Bear
